1
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,966
[Episode 18: The Dream is Over]

2
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,879
Xi Zhou.

3
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,680
Come on, give me a hug.

4
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,154
Dad, you're back.

5
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:26,000
Last time I saw you, you were only this tall.

6
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,443
It's been ten years. Look...

7
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,816
Eleven years.

8
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:34,444
That's right. You've grown up now.

9
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,120
- Hong Xia.
- Mom.

10
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:42,359
It's me. I'm back.

11
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:43,785
Why did you come back?

12
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,680
Xi Zhou's going to college.

13
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,844
I was thinking...

14
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:51,120
I missed her, so I came back.

15
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,062
When Xi Zhou was about six,

16
00:01:53,062 --> 00:01:54,680
you wanted to go out and start a business.

17
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:57,902
You took all our money and left without a word.

18
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,760
I called you so many times

19
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,360
and sent so many messages.

20
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:04,319
I waited for you every year.
But you never came back.

21
00:02:04,319 --> 00:02:07,079
You have no idea the gossip we endured.

22
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:09,800
Well, I was busy
trying to make money out there.

23
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,960
Busy?

24
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,960
Were you really so busy

25
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:14,639
that you couldn't even call me back?

26
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:17,199
We suffered so much all these years.

27
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:20,080
And you? You hid away and said nothing.

28
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,800
Now Xi Zhou is going to college,
and suddenly you're here.

29
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,406
What do you want?

30
00:02:23,406 --> 00:02:25,640
Get out of here, now.

31
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:26,920
Hong Xia.

32
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:29,479
Leaving you was on me.

33
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,880
But you don't know how hard it was

34
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,639
for me to make money out there.

35
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,400
I was afraid you'd blame me,

36
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,280
so I changed my number,

37
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,080
and I didn't dare to contact anyone.

38
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,840
I told myself

39
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,520
I must make it big

40
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:45,378
and make life good for both of you.

41
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,637
Look here.

42
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:50,768
Come and see.

43
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,240
How's this car?

44
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:58,159
Mom, his watch looks real.

45
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:59,919
It's mine, and yours.

46
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:06,407
Mom, should we believe him?

47
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,019
Don't buy into his bragging.

48
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,880
You two haven't eaten, right?

49
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:16,546
Well, let's go grab some food. Go.

50
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,879
People from our hometown told me

51
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:28,312
your restaurant is doing well.

52
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:30,719
You're a big boss now.

53
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:33,031
Is this little restaurant even a thing to you?

54
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:35,240
Hey, don't say that.

55
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:37,838
I thought of you both every day out there.

56
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:44,265
Xi Zhou's watching.

57
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,033
Let's go home.

58
00:03:59,553 --> 00:04:01,120
Here, let me help you.

59
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,247
Okay.

60
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,630
Give it to me.

61
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:18,493
<i>The first time I went on a joyride in the city.</i>

62
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:22,672
<i>The first time I saw my mom smile that happily.</i>

63
00:05:18,886 --> 00:05:20,640
<i>The first time...</i>

64
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,878
<i>I learned how scary lies could be.</i>

65
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:26,800
<i>He wove a dream out of lies</i>

66
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,782
<i>and took everything from us.</i>

67
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,506
<i>But</i>

68
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,226
<i>Mom,</i>

69
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,454
<i>the dream is over.</i>

70
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,676
<i>We can't stop lying anymore.</i>

71
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,400
<i>Are you with your dad?</i>

72
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:46,291
<i>Hello? Hello?</i>

73
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:48,197
Xi Zhou.

74
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,275
Why don't you just die?

75
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,917
You brat.

76
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,458
Xi Zhou.

77
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,680
Xi Zhou.

78
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,828
I know you hate me.

79
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,040
You were too young at that time.

80
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,959
You had no idea what I was going through.

81
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:11,240
Look how well you're doing now.

82
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,519
Just give me one million yuan.

83
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:14,023
And my project...

84
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:17,160
800,000 yuan will also do.

85
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,941
Xi Zhou, open the door.

86
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,320
Listen, I know an investor.

87
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:25,639
He's really interested in our land.

88
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:28,727
He offers a great price.

89
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,759
Last night I lost my temper

90
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:33,160
and argued with your mom.

91
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:35,600
But that's over. It's fine now.

92
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,000
Open the door. Let's talk.

93
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,120
Xi Zhou, open the door.

94
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:46,085
Xi Zhou, open the door!

95
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,451
Xi Zhou!

96
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:53,463
Fine. You're asking for trouble.

97
00:06:54,842 --> 00:06:56,240
Listen up, everyone.

98
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,680
I'm Ren Hong Xia's husband.

99
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,160
And Ren Xi Zhou's father.

100
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,959
These two are actually very poor.

101
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,806
Their clothes, food, and everything

102
00:07:04,806 --> 00:07:06,680
are all from some flea market.

103
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,920
They're putting on a rich act.

104
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,370
How shameless is that?

105
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,680
I've been away for many years.

106
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:16,762
Who knows if Ren Hong Xia's
been fooling around with other men?

107
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:19,399
Ren Xi Zhou, what are you doing?

108
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,560
Put the knife down.

109
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,639
I'm your father.

110
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:22,644
Get lost.

111
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,123
You ungrateful brat.

112
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:28,280
Just you wait. You'll regret it!

113
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,584
Get lost!

114
00:07:29,584 --> 00:07:31,800
Don't ever show your face
around me again. Get lost!

115
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,120
You'll regret it!

116
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:36,262
What are you looking at? Move!

117
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:41,915
Have you seen enough? Get out of here!

118
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,828
Let's go.

119
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:57,370
You went silent just now, so I ran over here.

120
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,810
I'm fine. Thank you.

121
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:02,860
You can leave now.

122
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:09,397
You... you don't want it anymore?

123
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:16,040
[Closed]
<i>Stay away from dangerous areas</i>

124
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,280
<i>to ensure the safety of life and property.</i>

125
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:20,560
<i>Heavy rainfall is on the way,</i>

126
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:23,199
<i>with accumulations up to 100 mm.</i>

127
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:25,319
<i>Please stay indoors if you live</i>

128
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:27,152
<i>in or near Nanwan.</i>

129
00:08:27,152 --> 00:08:28,840
Hello, Auntie Qiu.

130
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:29,879
Is my mom with you?

131
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,480
<i>No, she's not. What's wrong?</i>

132
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,280
Nothing. Her phone died.

133
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,834
I just wanted to know
if she's coming home tonight.

134
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,480
Thank you.

135
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,879
The back door is open.

136
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:42,120
Maybe your mom left
while you were talking to him.

137
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,480
Her phone is still inside.

138
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,320
We should call the police.

139
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,440
They won't help
until my mom's been missing 24 hours.

140
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:50,040
- Get out of my way.
- But we have to do something.

141
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,680
We can ask the others for help.

142
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,836
No need.

143
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,960
I know your pride won't let you.
I'll call them.

144
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,400
I've been humiliated enough today.

145
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,038
Don't make me look like a joke.

146
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:02,367
What if something happens to your mom?

147
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,440
I know how she is.

148
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:06,080
She hasn't been gone long. Nothing will happen.

149
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:08,131
You're the joke right now, you know that?

150
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:13,160
We're just poor people pretending to be rich.

151
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:15,919
To someone born into wealth like you,

152
00:09:15,919 --> 00:09:17,000
we do look like a joke.

153
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,031
That's not the point.

154
00:09:18,031 --> 00:09:19,720
You're actually enjoying this, aren't you?

155
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,640
What?

156
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:23,000
You've always loved showing off to me.

157
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,080
Online shopping, movie tickets, and your dad.

158
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,440
What does any of that have to do with me?

159
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:29,200
- I just--
- You couldn't beat me in school.

160
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,160
So you tried to prove you were superior

161
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:33,069
in every other way, didn't you?

162
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:40,276
I just considered you my friend.

163
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,280
Fine.

164
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,759
You win.

165
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:45,799
I'm the loser.

166
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:47,112
I'm the liar.

167
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,840
Feeling good about yourself now?

168
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,325
Can you drop the condescending pity?

169
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:54,840
Yes. I'm feeling good about myself.

170
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,399
I pity you.

171
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:58,662
Go wherever you want.

172
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:10,383
I don't care even if you die.

173
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:16,640
<i>Coupled with the astronomical tide,</i>

174
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:19,200
<i>the Nanwan coast will see rising water levels.</i>

175
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:21,879
<i>This could lead to water flooding</i>

176
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:24,520
<i>in some low-lying areas.</i>

177
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,160
<i>All relevant departments and residents</i>

178
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:28,268
<i>should take precautions.</i>

179
00:10:35,827 --> 00:10:36,879
You made it just in time.

180
00:10:36,879 --> 00:10:39,040
The garage will be flooded soon.

181
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:40,360
It won't get that bad.

182
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:42,515
You never know. It's a typhoon, after all.

183
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,910
Thank you, sir.

184
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:58,759
<i>The typhoon is coming.</i>

185
00:10:58,759 --> 00:11:00,800
<i>Take care of yourself and your mom.</i>

186
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,560
You're Mr. Xiang, right?

187
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:04,360
And you are?

188
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:07,019
I'm Jiang He, an actress
from Starlight Entertainment.

189
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:09,080
So it's Ms. Jiang.

190
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,280
I've heard so much about you.

191
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:12,640
You're too kind. I'm the admirer here.

192
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:15,135
Actually, we went to the same school.

193
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,799
I've seen all of your works,

194
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:29,000
and I really love them.

195
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:32,000
I've always hoped for a chance
to work with you.

196
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,759
I heard you were coming today.

197
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:36,800
So I talked my way into coming here
with the producer.

198
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,185
You don't mind, do you?

199
00:11:39,299 --> 00:11:40,312
Not at all.

200
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,360
I'm flattered, Ms. Jiang.

201
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:44,120
Thanks for your admiration.

202
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:46,025
Not for my love?

203
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:56,759
Come on, Mr. Xiang.

204
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:58,000
Let's have a drink together.

205
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,559
Cheers.

206
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:00,745
Cheers.

207
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:04,240
Mr. Xiang, I have a question.

208
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:07,080
Why is it an open ending?

209
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,519
They're still putting themselves first.

210
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,080
There hasn't been a chance

211
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:13,907
for either to make the first move.

212
00:12:13,907 --> 00:12:14,920
But you see,

213
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:19,440
the audience would love to see them...

214
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,879
Right, He?

215
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:23,880
Yeah, but leaving it open is also good.

216
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:26,440
It's classic Mr. Xiang.

217
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:28,440
You... you know each other?

218
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,879
He went to the same high school

219
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:31,040
as me, a year below.

220
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:33,187
Left a really deep impression on me.

221
00:12:33,187 --> 00:12:34,279
When I was in my second year,

222
00:12:34,279 --> 00:12:35,480
a girl came to tell me

223
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:37,200
not to have a romance with Mr. Xiang.

224
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,670
It was so funny.

225
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:42,920
A girl?

226
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,240
Yeah.

227
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:46,799
A spunky girl with a ponytail.

228
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:48,880
She was so earnest,

229
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:51,120
bowing and pleading.

230
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,759
I told her I didn't even know you.

231
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:54,159
Then she ran away

232
00:12:54,159 --> 00:12:56,000
with a red face.

233
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:58,077
Really, Mr. Xiang?

234
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:00,449
Mr. Xiang?

235
00:13:02,005 --> 00:13:03,593
How about you give it another thought?

236
00:13:03,593 --> 00:13:04,600
Okay.

237
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,666
Good.

238
00:13:11,519 --> 00:13:12,655
<i>Where's the list?</i>

239
00:13:12,655 --> 00:13:14,039
<i>Here.</i>

240
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:15,799
<i>So many people?</i>

241
00:13:15,799 --> 00:13:17,925
<i>Remove the unknowns.</i>

242
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,960
<i>Who's he?</i>

243
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,679
<i>Zhu Qiao Fei.</i>

244
00:13:21,679 --> 00:13:24,399
<i>Oh my gosh! I said we need good actors.</i>

245
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:26,679
<i>Why is he even on the list?</i>

246
00:13:26,679 --> 00:13:28,120
<i>Do you have his agent's number?</i>

247
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:30,240
<i>Tell them they don't need to come.</i>

248
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,960
<i>He only left his own.</i>

249
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,759
<i>Wait, the mic's on.</i>

250
00:13:33,759 --> 00:13:35,159
I'm Zhu Qiao Fei.

251
00:13:35,159 --> 00:13:37,003
<i>Next, number 24.</i>

252
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,480
Zhu Qiao Fei, come with me.

253
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,919
What's wrong? I'm at an interview.

254
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:47,279
Emergency! Hurry up!

255
00:13:47,279 --> 00:13:49,360
- I can't. The interview is about to start.
- Do it later.

256
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,986
Do it later!

257
00:13:53,559 --> 00:13:55,240
Sorry, Mr. Xiang.

258
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,279
The typhoon is coming.

259
00:13:56,279 --> 00:13:57,440
I have a flight to catch.

260
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,160
And I'll have to say goodbye here.

261
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:00,302
Okay.

262
00:14:05,799 --> 00:14:07,692
Mr. Xiang, be careful on the way.

263
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,725
Hello?

264
00:14:16,519 --> 00:14:18,953
There's an emergency at Ren Xizhou's. Hurry!

265
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,760
Look, someone's walking into the sea.

266
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,880
Who is that?

267
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,374
It's dangerous!

268
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,919
Make way, please.

269
00:14:48,919 --> 00:14:50,092
Mom!

270
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:53,727
Mom! If you're there, say something!

271
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,511
Come back!

